               <sense xml:id="Dmain" xml:lang="la" source="#dillmann"> quadril. I [cognatum cum <foreign xml:lang="gez">አብደ፡</foreign> q.v., <foreign xml:lang="ar">أَبِدَ</foreign> <cit type="translation" xml:lang="la"><t:quote xmlns:t="http://www.tei-c.org/ns/1.0"> iratus </t:quote></cit> et <cit type="translation" xml:lang="la"><t:quote xmlns:t="http://www.tei-c.org/ns/1.0"> efferatus fuit </t:quote></cit>, <foreign xml:lang="ar">أَبَدَ</foreign> <cit type="translation" xml:lang="la"><t:quote xmlns:t="http://www.tei-c.org/ns/1.0"> ferum evasit animal </t:quote></cit>, <foreign xml:lang="ar">عَرْبَدَ</foreign> <cit type="translation" xml:lang="la"><t:quote xmlns:t="http://www.tei-c.org/ns/1.0"> pravum et malignum se ostendit </t:quote></cit>] <cit type="translation" xml:lang="la"><t:quote xmlns:t="http://www.tei-c.org/ns/1.0"> furere et refractarium esse </t:quote></cit>: <foreign xml:lang="gez">ከመ፡ እጐልት፡ እንተ፡ ተሀረብድ፡ ሀርበደ፡ ኤፍሬም፡</foreign> <foreign xml:lang="grc">ὡς δάμαλις παροιστρῶσα παροίστρησεν Ἰσραηλ</foreign> <ref cRef="Hos." loc="4,16">Hos. 4,16</ref>; <cit type="translation" xml:lang="la"><t:quote xmlns:t="http://www.tei-c.org/ns/1.0"> scortatio efficit hominem </t:quote></cit> <foreign xml:lang="gez">ከመ፡ ሐረውያ፡ ዘሀርበደ፡</foreign> <cit type="translation" xml:lang="la"><t:quote xmlns:t="http://www.tei-c.org/ns/1.0"> instar apris furentis </t:quote></cit>, <ref cRef="Org." loc="6.">Org. 6.</ref> (<cit type="translation" xml:lang="la"><t:quote xmlns:t="http://www.tei-c.org/ns/1.0"> Ludolfus </t:quote></cit>ex conjectura: <cit type="translation" xml:lang="la"><t:quote xmlns:t="http://www.tei-c.org/ns/1.0"> volutavit se in coeno </t:quote></cit>). – <lbl expand="Vocabularium Aethiopicum, -a -a">Voc. Ae.</lbl>: <foreign xml:lang="gez">ሐርበደ፡ ዘ፡ አበደ፡</foreign> </sense>
               
